216
00:09:00.748 --> 00:09:02.165
No.

217
00:09:02.166 --> 00:09:03.458
I got it.

218
00:09:03.459 --> 00:09:06.002
Go. Dr. Collins.

219
00:09:06.003 --> 00:09:07.462
Okay. Natalie.

220
00:09:07.463 --> 00:09:10.257
