802
00:30:52.475 --> 00:30:54.059
<i>I mean. there's tons of people.</i>

803
00:30:54.060 --> 00:30:55.602
<i>and there's a lot
of cool stuff going on.</i>

804
00:30:55.603 --> 00:30:57.062
