a good time.

805
00:30:57.063 --> 00:30:58.772
How's your friend?

806
00:30:58.773 --> 00:31:01.066
<i>Oh. she actually wanted
to thank you personally.</i>

807
00:31:01.067 --> 00:31:02.651
<i>Hi. Dr. Robinavitch!</i>

808
00:31:02.652 --> 00:31:04.444
Just Robby.

809
00:31:04.445 --> 00:31:06.613
<i>Robby. I'm Leah. Jake's friend.</i>

810
00:31:06.614 --> 00:31:08.240
- <i>Girlfriend.</i>
